Editor’s note: This is the first installment in an occasional series called Maine Acts of Kindness, highlighting volunteer and philanthropic efforts during the pandemic.
Participating restaurants deliver free meals to health care workers, first responders and others at the front line of battling the pandemic, along with those at high risk during virus outbreak.
